high_descs: Take a left turn to reach the bookshelf on the right of the coffeetable.
Pick up the newspaper from the top of the shelf.
Face the middle shelf of the shelf.
Put the newspaper in the middle shelf.
Turn around to face the box on the grey ottoman on the sofa.
Pick up the newspaper from the box.
Turn right to head to the shelf.
Put the newspaper in the middle shelf of the bookshelf.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers in the middle shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, walk all the way to the upper right corner of the hall in front of the tall coffeetable.
Pick up a newspaper from the top of the tall stand.
Take a small step back from the shelf.
Put the newspaper in the bottom of the tall shelf.
Turn around and walk up to a sofa on your right that is near a table.
Pick up a newspaper from the bench.
Go back to the tall shelf.
Place the newspaper next to another in the bottom of the tall shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspaper in the bottom of the tall shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the side table next to the coffeetable.
Pick up the newspaper on the side table.
Position yourself to reach the lower shelf on the side table.
Put the newspaper on the lower shelf on the side table.
Turn around and go to the sofa.
Take the newspaper out of the box.
Turn right and go back to the shelf.
Put the newspaper on the lower shelf of the side table.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers on the Shelf next to the couch.
